                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "You're the one pulling the strings, aren't you? Working with Viktor."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "Viktor provides security. I provide the future. Our arrangement is mutually beneficial and scientifically sound."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Your 'future' is built on corpses. I'm ending this."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "You lack the perspective to understand what is at stake. My research cannot be interrupted by emotional outbursts."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "It's already interrupted. Step aside, or be stepped over."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
